1. Moja sestra je u *razredu* sa vašim sinom. (My sister is in the same grade as your son.)
2. Danas sam se upoznao sa *razredom* novih studenata. (Today I met the group of new students.)
3. Naša škola je po kvalitetu nastave među *razredima* u vrhu. (Our school is among the top in terms of teaching quality among grades.)
4. Učiteljica je pregledala zadatke i dala pohvale najboljim *razredima*. (The teacher reviewed the assignments and gave praise to the best grades.)
5. Nisam mogao da se setim kojoj *razred* pripadao taj đak. (I couldn't remember which grade that student belonged to.)
6. Moja kćerka voli da uči matematiku i u *razredu* je najbolja u toj oblasti. (My daughter likes to learn math and she is the best in that subject in her grade.)
7. Najbolji *razredi* će biti nagrađeni na kraju školske godine. (The best grades will be rewarded at the end of the school year.)
8. Kada su proslavili svoj uspeh na takmičenju, *razred* je bio presrećan. (When they celebrated their success at the competition, the grade was overjoyed.)
9. Ovaj udžbenik se koristi u osmom *razredu* osnovne škole. (This textbook is used in eighth grade of elementary school.)
10. *Razredni* starešina je odgovoran za vaspitno-obrazovni rad u razredu. (The homeroom teacher is responsible for educational work in the grade.)